        "\n",
        "def include_outliers(df=df, num_cols=num_col, lower_fence=lower_fence, upper_fence=upper_fence):\n",
        "  exist_outliers = dict()\n",
        "  for col in num_col:\n",
        "    if ((df[col]>upper_fence[col]).any()) or ((df[col]<lower_fence[col]).any()):\n",
        "      exist_outliers[col]=True\n",
        "\n",
        "  return exist_outliers"
      ],
